<p>I would suggest NEVER using 3 songs on one macro key.&nbsp;&nbsp;Keep it one song per key. <br /> <br />example: <br />/st <br />/cast # <br /> <br />Nothing else. /st is all you need to stop a song.  Replace # with the appropriate song gem number. <br /> <br />For more good info, and a good start point for bards see the bard faq at eqdiva.com under the Guides section (menu to the left of screen). <br />Also a direct link to it in thread Bard FAQ here on Alla's. <br /> <br /><i><span class="sm">Edited, Tue Jun  8 05:54:33 2004 by bdfoster</span></i></p>
